{"word":"ἴσχιον","slug":"ἴσχιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n51313\" key=\"i)/sxion\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴσχῐ-ον</orth> (parox.), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <sense id=\"n51313.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hip-joint</tr_>, in which the thigh turns, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κατ᾽ ἰσχίον, ἔνθα τε μηρὸς ἰσχίῳ ἐνστρέφεται, κοτύλην δέ τέ μιν καλέουσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:305\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.305</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:339\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.339</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:234\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.234</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; later <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ κατ᾽ ἰσχίον ἄρθρον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0057.tlg017:15:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ UP\">UP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.8</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also, the intra-capsular ligament of the hip-joint, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:2:186\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.186</biblScope> </bibl>; <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"gree